------------------------------------
Class BSRecod:

    def __init__(self, bs_file_paths):
        self.bs_file_paths = bs_file_paths
        
    def bsrecord(self):
        for bs_file_path in self.bs_file_paths:
		print(bs_file_path)

		accounting_standard = px.get_AccountingStandard(bs_file_path)

            	if accounting_standard == "IFRS":
            		bs_common_printer.print_bs_common_info(bs_file_path)
            		bs_ifrs_printer.print_bs_ifrs_info(bs_file_path)
            		bs_db_record.create_bs_db_record(bs_file_path)

		elif accounting_standard == "Japan GAAP":
			bs_common_printer.print_bs_common_info(bs_file_path)
			bs_japan_gaap_printer.print_bs_japan_gaap_info(bs_file_path)
			bs_db_record.create_bs_db_record(bs_file_path)
            	else:
			bs_common_printer.print_bs_common_info(bs_file_path)
			bs_db_record.create_bs_db_record(bs_file_path)

---------------------------------------------------



今後やりたいこと。

命名規則の適用

Classは大文字で始める。

モジュールと関数は全て小文字

ファイルがモジュール

関数は動詞_名詞
モジュールは名詞